{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create me a product carousel that has the following features:
    
    - Title (above the carousel) with rich text editor
    - Product name and price display under each product picture 
    - Pulls first product image by default for each product but gives you option for each product to upload a custom image to replace instead. if no custom image is uploaded, it displays the first product image
    - controls for how many products a row will display on desktop, tablet, and mobile
    - top right of carousel has buttons to move one product to left or right. The buttons should be small maroon carets with black outline circles around them 
    - should show second product image on hover (even when custom image is used)
    - ability to display vendor (toggle on/off)
    - ability to display product rating (toggle on/off
    - quick add (options for none, standard, and bulk)
    - border bottom (toggle on/off)
    - padding top slider
    - padding bottom slider
    - standard or card style display in theme settings
    - color scheme in theme settings
    - page width in theme settings
    
    This is a very similar block you can use as a starting point to build (only change what's needed):
    
    {%- style -%}
      #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
        position: relative;
        --padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px;
        --padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    
        {%- if section.settings.border_top -%}
          border-top: 1px solid #CCC;
        {%- endif -%}
      }
    
      {% if section.settings.border_bottom %}
        #shopify-section-{{ section.id }}::after {
          border-bottom: 1px solid #C6C6C6;
          content: '';
          display: block;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 700px;
          height: 0px;
          display: block;
          position: absolute;
          bottom: 0;
          left: 50%;
          transform: translateX(-50%);
    
          @media (max-width: 768px) {
            max-width: calc(100% - 3rem);
          }
        }
      {% endif %}
    
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
          --padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top | divided_by: 2 }}px;
          --padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom | divided_by: 2 }}px;
        }
    
        #shopify-section-{{ section.id }}{
          border-top: 0px solid #CCC;
        }
    
        .es-font-h2.center{
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    {%- endstyle -%}
    
